Rules.InvariantScript:
If (
    Or(
        App.ActiveScreen = nav_bar.homeScreen,
        App.ActiveScreen = nav_bar.inspectScreen,
        App.ActiveScreen = nav_bar.browseScreen,
        App.ActiveScreen = nav_bar.supportScreen
    ), register_grey, register_red
)

If (
    Or(
        App.ActiveScreen = nav_bar.homeScreen,
        App.ActiveScreen = nav_bar.inspectScreen,
        App.ActiveScreen = nav_bar.browseScreen,
        App.ActiveScreen = nav_bar.supportScreen
    ), Color.Gray, Color.Red
)
